features: ⭐【Package Content】：Include a roll of 30m x 80cm of star cellophane paper. Cellophane wrap looks like it's 40cm wide, but in fact its width is folded by a half, and when you unfold it, it's 80cm wide
⭐【Unique design】:White star and hollow star printed,the design will make gift more pretty and shining.And it is a joy to wrap gifts in lovely wrapping paper.
⭐【Recyclable】：Christmas gift wrapping paper are 100% recyclable and eco-friendly material. And the paper are thick and won’t tear when wrapping gift.
⭐【Widely Application】:Cellophane wrapping paper can be used for decorating gift bags or wrapping present or bouquet . The best choice for Christmas, birthday, party, festivals and so on.
⭐【Multi-Purpose】: Perfect for wrapping your Christmas, wedding or birthday gifts, also suit for crafts, arts, table cover and more.
⭐【Please note】:The cellophane is folded in half. When you unfold the paper, you will find that it is 80cm wide
